  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Cholera
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    Vibrio cholerae
Transmission:Contaminated water
Symptoms:    Profuse watery diarrhea, vomiting
Treatment:   Oral rehydration, antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   0.095M
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  1854

Disease:     Influenza
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Influenza viruses
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, chills, muscle aches
Treatment:   Oseltamivir, rest, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     Yes (annual update)
Discovered:  1933

Disease:     Dengue
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Dengue virus
Transmission:Aedes mosquito
Symptoms:    Fever, severe joint pain, rash
Treatment:   Supportive care, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.04M
Vaccine:     Yes (for previously infected)
Discovered:  1779

